---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import TrustedBy from '../components/TrustedBy.astro';
---
<Layout
	title="Catering Surrey BC | Indian Catering for Weddings, Corporate Events"
	description="Indian catering Surrey BC for weddings, corporate events, and private parties. Halal, vegan, vegetarian. Award-winning since 2010. Delivery across all Surrey neighbourhoods."
	canonical="/catering-surrey"
	ogImage="https://sulacatering.com/uploads/wedding-catering.webp"
>

	<Fragment slot="schema">
		<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
			"@context": "https://schema.org","@type": "Service",
			"name": "Catering Surrey",
			"provider": {"@id": "https://sulacatering.com/#organization"},
			"areaServed": {"@type": "City", "name": "Surrey"},
			"serviceType": "Indian Catering"
		})} />
	</Fragment>

	<section class="hero" style="background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(20,8,16,0.85) 0%, rgba(38,14,38,0.7) 50%, rgba(20,8,16,0.9) 100%), url('/uploads/Indian-food-catering-vancouver-burnaby-richmond-office.webp');">
		<div class="hero-content">
			<h1>Catering<br/>in <em>Surrey</em></h1>
			<p class="hero-tagline">Indian catering across Surrey, Newton, Guildford, Cloverdale, South Surrey, Whalley. Award-winning since 2010.</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<TrustedBy />


	<section class="section section-cream">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="intro-block reveal">
				<h2>Indian Catering for <em>Surrey Events</em></h2>
				<div class="gold-divider-ornament"><span></span><div class="diamond"></div><span></span></div>
				<p>Surrey is home to one of the largest South Asian communities in Canada. The bar for catering here is set by the families themselves, who know exactly how a sangeet should taste and exactly when the chai should land. That's the bar we cook to. Grand Taj <a href="/weddings" class="body-link">wedding catering</a>, Aria receptions, home Diwali parties in Newton, corporate lunches in Guildford. Our menus draw on North Indian, South Indian, Hyderabadi, and Goan traditions, the same way our restaurants have for fifteen years.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<img src="/uploads/vancouver-catering-companies-weddings.webp" alt="Indian wedding catering Surrey" class="full-width-image" loading="lazy" />

	<section class="section section-cream">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="text-center reveal">
				<p class="eyebrow">What We Cater in Surrey</p>
				<h2 class="mag-title">Every <em>Surrey Event</em></h2>
				<div class="gold-divider-ornament"><span></span><div class="diamond"></div><span></span></div>
			</div>
			<div class="service-grid-v2">
				<a href="/weddings" class="service-card-v2 reveal">
					<div class="service-card-img">
						<img src="/uploads/wedding-catering-vancouver-bc.webp" alt="Wedding catering Surrey" loading="lazy" />
						<div class="service-card-overlay">
							<span class="service-eyebrow">Surrey Weddings</span>
							<h3>Wedding <em>Catering</em></h3>
							<p>South Asian weddings at Grand Taj, Aria, and home venues across Surrey. Halal, vegetarian, vegan, Jain.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</a>
				<a href="/corporate" class="service-card-v2 reveal delay-100">
					<div class="service-card-img">
						<img src="/uploads/indian-food-catering-vancouver-corporate.webp" alt="Corporate catering Surrey" loading="lazy" />
						<div class="service-card-overlay">
							<span class="service-eyebrow">Guildford · Cloverdale</span>
							<h3>Corporate <em>Catering</em></h3>
							<p>Office lunches and conference catering for Surrey's tech parks and corporate buildings.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</a>
				<a href="/private-parties" class="service-card-v2 reveal delay-200">
					<div class="service-card-img">
						<img src="/uploads/indian-restaurant-catering-private-party.webp" alt="Private party Surrey" loading="lazy" />
						<div class="service-card-overlay">
							<span class="service-eyebrow">Newton · South Surrey</span>
							<h3>Private <em>Parties</em></h3>
							<p>Birthdays, anniversaries, Diwali, housewarmings, at homes across every Surrey neighbourhood.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</a>
				<a href="/cafe-catering" class="service-card-v2 reveal delay-300">
					<div class="service-card-img">
						<img src="/uploads/indian-food-catering-near-me-vancouver-bc.webp" alt="Cafe catering Surrey" loading="lazy" />
						<div class="service-card-overlay">
							<span class="service-eyebrow">Chai · Coffee · Pastries</span>
							<h3>Café <em>Catering</em></h3>
							<p>Live masala chai bars and specialty coffee for Surrey weddings, conferences, brunches.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section section-plum pattern-mandala">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="experience">
				<div class="experience-img reveal-left">
					<img src="/uploads/best-caterer-vancouver.webp" alt="South Asian Indian catering Surrey" loading="lazy" />
				</div>
				<div class="experience-content reveal-right">
					<h2>We Know <em>Surrey</em></h2>
					<p>The thing about a Surrey wedding is that the auntie network does QA in real time. We've been QA'd plenty. The chicken either tastes right or it doesn't, the chana is either correct or it isn't, the chai is either how it should be or someone tells someone. Fifteen years in, we still make sure it's right.</p>
					<p>For bigger weddings of 300+, we coordinate directly with venue managers and your decorator. We also cater across <a href="/catering-vancouver" class="body-link">Vancouver</a>, <a href="/catering-burnaby" class="body-link">Burnaby</a>, and <a href="/catering-richmond" class="body-link">Richmond</a>.</p>
					<div class="experience-stats">
						<div class="stat-item"><div class="stat-number">500+</div><div class="stat-label">Max Capacity</div></div>
						<div class="stat-item"><div class="stat-number">$5</div><div class="stat-label">Flat Delivery</div></div>
						<div class="stat-item"><div class="stat-number">2010</div><div class="stat-label">Established</div></div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section section-cream">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="text-center reveal">
				<p class="eyebrow">Common Questions</p>
				<h2 class="mag-title">Surrey Catering <em>FAQs</em></h2>
				<div class="gold-divider-ornament"><span></span><div class="diamond"></div><span></span></div>
			</div>
			<div class="faq-list">
				<div class="faq-item reveal"><h3>Do you cater Surrey wedding banquet halls?</h3><p>Yes, Grand Taj, Aria, and most major Surrey banquet halls. We coordinate with venue managers on setup and timeline.</p></div>
				<div class="faq-item reveal"><h3>How fast is delivery to Surrey?</h3><p>Delivery to Surrey runs 35 to 45 minutes from our Vancouver kitchens, depending on traffic. Temperature-controlled transport keeps food hot.</p></div>
				<div class="faq-item reveal"><h3>Can you cater large Surrey weddings of 500+ guests?</h3><p>Yes, we regularly cater large South Asian weddings, with experienced staff for large-format service.</p></div>
				<div class="faq-item reveal"><h3>Is Surrey delivery extra?</h3><p>$5 flat delivery, no minimum order, same as Vancouver.</p></div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>


</Layout>
